# =============================================================================
# LLM Provider API Keys for Integration Tests
# =============================================================================
#
# Copy this file to .env and add your actual API keys:
#   cp .env.example .env
#   # Edit .env with your actual keys
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit .env to git! It's already in .gitignore
#
# =============================================================================
# Core Providers
# =============================================================================

# Anthropic (Claude)
# Get your key from: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Format: sk-ant-api03-...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key-here

# OpenAI (GPT-4, GPT-3.5, etc.)
# Get your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Format: sk-...
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here

# Google Gemini
# Get your key from: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# Format: AIza...
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Specialized Providers
# =============================================================================

# Perplexity AI (Web Search)
# Get your key from: https://www.perplexity.ai/settings/api
# Format: pplx-...
PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=your-perplexity-api-key-here

# OpenRouter (LLM API Aggregator)
# Get your key from: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# Format: sk-or-v1-...
# Note: OpenRouter can access multiple providers with a single key
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-openrouter-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# European & Sovereignty Providers
# =============================================================================

# Mistral AI
# Get your key from: https://console.mistral.ai/
# Format: varies
MISTRAL_API_KEY=your-mistral-api-key-here

# Apertus (Switzerland, EU Digital Sovereignty)
# Get your key from: https://apertus.ai/
# Format: varies
# Note: Multilingual, GDPR-compliant, EU data sovereignty
APERTUS_API_KEY=your-apertus-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Chinese Providers
# =============================================================================

# Qwen (Alibaba Cloud)
# Get your key from: https://dashscope.console.aliyun.com/
# Format: sk-...
QWEN_API_KEY=your-qwen-api-key-here

# Baidu ERNIE
# Get your key from: https://cloud.baidu.com/
# Format: varies
# Note: Requires both API key and secret key
BAIDU_API_KEY=your-baidu-api-key-here
BAIDU_SECRET_KEY=your-baidu-secret-key-here

# Zhipu GLM
# Get your key from: https://open.bigmodel.cn/
# Format: varies
ZHIPU_API_KEY=your-zhipu-api-key-here

# DeepSeek AI
# Get your key from: https://platform.deepseek.com/
# Format: varies
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-deepseek-api-key-here

# Kimi (Moonshot AI)
# Get your key from: https://platform.moonshot.cn/
# Format: varies
KIMI_API_KEY=your-kimi-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Other Providers
# =============================================================================

# MinMax AI
# Get your key from: https://platform.minmax.ai/
# Format: varies
MINMAX_API_KEY=your-minmax-api-key-here

# Grok (xAI)
# Get your key from: https://console.x.ai/
# Format: xai-...
GROK_API_KEY=your-grok-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Optional: Provider-Specific Configuration
# =============================================================================

# OpenRouter Base URL (if using custom endpoint)
# OPENROUTER_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1

# Anthropic Base URL (if using proxy or custom endpoint)
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com

# OpenAI Base URL (if using proxy or custom endpoint)
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1

# =============================================================================
# Usage Notes
# =============================================================================
#
# For integration tests, you typically only need one provider key.
# The tests will use ANTHROPIC_API_KEY by default.
#
# To use a different provider, modify the test or set the appropriate
# environment variable.
#
# Example:
#   export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY="sk-ant-api03-..."
#   cargo test --test integration_prompt_formatting -- --ignored
#
# =============================================================================
# Data Sovereignty & Compliance Notes
# =============================================================================
#
# Some providers offer data sovereignty guarantees:
# - Apertus: Switzerland, GDPR-compliant
# - Baidu, Zhipu, Qwen: China (data stays in China)
# - Mistral: EU-based options available
#
# Use AgentRequirements.with_data_sovereignty() to specify requirements.
# Use AgentRequirements.with_compliance() for GDPR, SOC2, HIPAA, etc.
#
